srengine.utils

Class SortedList<V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • srengine.utils.SortedList<V>

  • public class SortedList<V>
extends java.lang.Object
    SortedList is list of integer keys and values which type can vary and must be specified by in template. SortedList is sorted ascending by keys with every newly added value and key pair. If no key provided, it will be set to zero. If amount of value-key pairs reaches maximum capacity, size doubles.
    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
    Vojtech 'Rain' Vladyka
